                            <span class="cputimer_focus_icon">↔</span>
                            <span class="cputimer_focus_text"><strong>Note:</strong> Toggling outputs accesses target registers via the debugger, which may briefly shift focus to the source editor. Click the <strong>CDT tab</strong> to return.</span>
                        </div>
